    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clash with hordes of increasingly more difficult enemies, fighting back with powerful items and abilities. Explore different builds and classes, discover new items, and re-play with several ramping difficulty levels in this exciting arcadey shoot 'em up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248610/extras/f86e1f986304870033d049e450d969ae.webp?t=1731348620\" width=780 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248610/extras/56f676b89b873e717f4f8e95e12feb67.avif?t=1731348620\" width=750 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bullet Rogue features a variety of several different enemy types each more challenging than the last. Fight through waves as these enemies as they swarm from all directions and unload their weaponry upon you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248610/extras/f620b1e59d70da38422ef83d2a29b247.webp?t=1731348620\" width=750 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248610/extras/837b943ccb0c80d0a7214f834ba5bd95.avif?t=1731348620\" width=750 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover a wide variety of items with differing effects and rarities. Fuse specific items together to unlock new more powerful items. Create different builds with the items that you discover in your run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248610/extras/32fe848d042154a09ef4725648ab33e6.webp?t=1731348620\" width=750 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3248610/extras/e1a56c5024d5cc5b33e3472311794855.avif?t=1731348620\" width=750 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with different visual styles. The different styles make it feel like a completely different game and some will offer an interesting challenge by virtue of making it more difficult to discern shapes and colors.</p>",
